      "contentHtml": "<p>Wiping your Transience save files solves LowLevelFatalError launch issue. Also allows you to restart from complete scratch.</p>\n<h1>Step 1: Disable Steam Cloud for Transience.</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>Locate Transience in your Steam library.</li>\n<li>Right click &gt; Properties</li>\n<li>Disable Steam Cloud</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"/images/cloud_save.png\" alt=\"Steam Cloud setting\" loading=\"lazy\" /></p>\n<h1>Step 2: Delete AppData/Local/HyperAware/Saved folder</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>Press <strong>Win + R</strong> and type <strong>\"AppData\"</strong></li>\n<li>Open the <strong>\"Local\"</strong> folder.</li>\n<li>Locate and open the <strong>\"HyperAware\"</strong> folder.</li>\n<li>Delete the <strong>\"Saved\"</strong> folder.</li>\n</ul>\n<h1>Step 3: Boot the game</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>Reboot the game and you should find yourself at the startup process again.</li>\n</ul>\n<h1>Step 4 (Optional): Re-enable Steam Cloud</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>Only do this after you've reopened the game and closed it again.</li>\n</ul>",
